   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">A program is a collection of proposed and authorized projects.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">A program provides a comprehensive view of project requirements and available funds.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Program</uicontrol> form enables you to: <ul class="- topic/ul ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">Add multiple planned projects  to a program</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Group projects under a program and assign funds</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">View funds that are available, remaining, andrequired</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">View details of each fund category and fund source</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">View the forecast of the program over the program period</li>
            <li class="- topic/li "> Perform what-if analysis by creating multiple program scenarios and selecting the best scenario for approval</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Performwhat-if analysisusing fund views</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Create snapshots for comparison</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Approve projects </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Manage program revisions</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Generate reports</li>
         </ul>
      </p>
